      "review_summary": "The PR exports `checkPortInUse` from `src/infra/ports-inspect.ts` and rewires CLI `isPortBusy` to return whether that shared multi-host probe reports `busy`.\n\nPR surface: Source -8. Total -8 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main and `v2026.6.9` still use a hostless `isPortBusy` bind, and `forceFreePortAndWait` exits early when that helper reports free. I did not run a live socket reproduction in this read-only review.",
